---
title: Chermoula Pan-Seared Chicken with Pearl Couscous & Lemon Yoghurt
description: It’s chicken tonight and on the menu we have luxurious chicken, seared, spiced and smothered with a zappy lemon yoghurt. Let’s not stop there though, a nutty apple salad and fluffy couscous elevate the dish with flavour and nutrition. You’ll want your chicken like this for every meal!

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with pearl couscous due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your
recipe card!*
